          "expr": "100 * sum by (operation) (rate(floatchat_redis_cache_hits_total[5m])) / clamp_min(sum by (operation) (rate(floatchat_redis_cache_hits_total[5m])) + sum by (operation) (rate(floatchat_redis_cache_misses_total[5m])), 1e-9)",
